you're a loser, yeah?

00:40.306 --> 00:42.176
What? Did I say
he thinks I'm a loser?

00:42.209 --> 00:43.846
Do you think
he thinks I'm a loser?

00:43.879 --> 00:45.450
Yo. You guys okay?

00:45.483 --> 00:46.886
SWEEPS AND EBRA:
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:46.919 --> 00:48.322
Any of it salvageable?

00:48.355 --> 00:49.858
-SWEEPS: No.
-EBRA: Yes.

00:49.891 --> 00:51.027
-Yes.
-Fuck.

00:51.060 --> 00:53.165
Look, it's probably hard
for your dad to be supportive

00:53.198 --> 00:55.637
because he doesn't understand
that this job doesn't pay much.

00:55.670 --> 00:57.274
It doesn't amount
to anything and, uh,

00:57.307 --> 00:59.177
it doesn't make
a whole lot of sense,
you know.

00:59.210 --> 01:01.515
