-Too few.

01:51.715 --> 01:52.951
What? I promise you,

01:52.984 --> 01:54.388
there aren't
too few forks, Sugar.

01:54.421 --> 01:55.222
SUGAR:
Okay, this is productive.

01:55.256 --> 01:57.059
I can't wait
to talk about spoons.

01:57.092 --> 01:58.027
-Hey, where's the phone?
-Oh.

01:58.061 --> 01:59.932
Marcus just broke it.
Can you order a new one?

01:59.965 --> 02:01.569
Sure. You can
shove it up your ass.

02:01.602 --> 02:02.604
I need to talk to you later.

02:02.637 --> 02:04.006
Thank you.

02:05.309 --> 02:06.210
