a hollow in my head ♪

07:50.733 --> 07:52.503
♪ I'm just checking it up ♪

07:52.837 --> 07:55.709
♪ Baby,
one more time for you ♪

07:56.143 --> 08:00.586
♪ Checking it up
until the pile hits the sky ♪

08:02.490 --> 08:06.397
♪ It's like I think
I'm sick of cocaine ♪

08:06.898 --> 08:08.936
♪ But I got a feeling like
it's running... ♪

08:08.969 --> 08:10.439
CARMY:
Wait. Wait, wait, wait.

08:11.608 --> 08:13.512
♪ I'm just checking it up ♪

08:13.545 --> 08:16.385
♪ Baby, one more time
for you ♪

08:16.418 --> 08:18.322
-CARMY: Okay.
-SYDNEY: Okay.

08:18.355 --> 08:21.494
♪ Checking it up until
the pile hits the sky ♪

08:22.128 --> 08:23.699
♪ Well,
even the best years... ♪

08:23.732 --> 08:25.669
Hell of a lot
of Sydneys in here.

08:27.038 --> 08:28.608
Don't look 'em in the eyes.

08:34.086 --> 08:36.892
♪ All these seasons ♪

08:36.925 --> 08:39.063
♪ All this time ♪

08:39.096 --> 08:43.739
♪ Spinning past till they
leave you far behind ♪

08:43.772 --> 08:44.808
♪ Lay me down... ♪

08:44.841 --> 08:46.612
SYDNEY:
Just thinking like... (tuts)

08:46.645 --> 08:50.319
...beef, uh, smoke, cherry.

08:50.352 --> 08:51.822
That sort of world.

08:51.855 --> 08:52.991
I like that.

08:53.024 --> 08:54.727
SYDNEY:
Still thinking chaos menu?

08:55.228 --> 08:56.965
Yeah, chaos menu, but, um...

08:58.368 --> 08:59.504
uh, thoughtful.

08:59.537 --> 09:00.639
SYDNEY: Hmm.

09:02.543 --> 09:05.516
♪ ♪

09:09.122 --> 09:11.728
-(Carmy chuckles)
-Really?

09:11.761 --> 09:13.566
-CARMY: It's New York.
-SYDNEY: Hmm.

09:13.599 --> 09:14.634
CARMY: Lame, right?

09:14.667 --> 09:15.536
I wanna hate it,

09:15.569 --> 09:17.640
like, don't get me wrong,
I do, but...

09:18.842 --> 09:20.713
(winces) Looks sick.

09:20.746 --> 09:22.616
And I bet it felt
really good wearing it.

09:23.785 --> 09:25.054
-Yeah, it did.
-SYDNEY: Hmm.

09:27.460 --> 09:29.431
Can I ask you something

09:29.464 --> 09:31.701
and you can tell me
to fuck off if you want?

09:32.270 --> 09:33.872
I doubt I'm gonna
tell you to fuck off.

09:33.905 --> 09:34.941
SYDNEY: Hmm. Uh...

09:34.974 --> 09:36.645
When you got that call,

09:36.678 --> 09:37.780
the three-star call...

09:37.813 --> 09:39.149
-Fuck off.
-SYDNEY: Yeah, okay.

09:39.182 --> 09:40.720
Yeah.

09:40.753 --> 09:42.757
-CARMY: Um...
-I don't know.

09:42.790 --> 09:43.825
How did it feel?

09:43.859 --> 09:46.431
