10:35.863 --> 10:38.134
You can see just fine
from where you are.

10:38.167 --> 10:40.171
-Okay.
-It's my ladder.

10:40.204 --> 10:41.608
FAK: Yeah, okay.

10:46.016 --> 10:48.221
Oh, you're such
a fuckin' showoff.

10:48.255 --> 10:49.357
(Fak laughs)

10:49.391 --> 10:52.029
-Think you're so fuckin' cool?
-I am so fuckin' cool.

10:52.062 --> 10:53.966
-And you don't need to be here.
-I'm the supervisor.

10:53.999 --> 10:55.201
-Supervisor of what?
-FAK: Not good, guys.

10:55.234 --> 10:56.505
This is not good.

10:56.538 --> 10:57.540
-This is not good.
-What's not good?

10:57.573 --> 10:58.575
-Mold.
-MARCUS: Is that bad?

10:58.608 --> 10:59.610
Mold is the death knell.

10:59.643 --> 11:01.782
Don't freak out
and go calling for Mom, okay?

11:01.815 --> 11:03.519
This is scary.
This could ruin everything.

11:03.552 --> 11:04.921
Listen, it is scary, okay?

11:04.954 --> 11:06.992
And I will grant you
that it's gained some traction

11:07.025 --> 11:08.127
in recent media cycles.

11:08.160 --> 11:09.931
Mold is a buzzword,
yeah, for sure.

11:09.964 --> 11:11.735
But if you go call Mom,
she's gonna call in

11:11.768 --> 11:13.472
all the weirdos
and the scientists,

11:13.505 --> 11:14.741
the abatement people.

11:14.774 --> 11:16.712
Lest I remind you,

11:16.745 --> 11:19.583
we are on
cousin's schedule,
Neil Geoff.

11:20.318 --> 11:21.922
-What's your middle name?
-What's my middle name?

11:21.955 --> 11:23.859
-Yeah, like,
what's your middle name?
-Lawrence.

11:23.892 --> 11:26.130
Well, Richard Lawrence,
I'm telling Mom now.

11:26.163 --> 11:27.867
Don't you fucking dare.

11:27.900 --> 11:29.069
I'm gonna call Mom right now.

11:29.102 --> 11:30.673
-Don't you fucking dare.
-I dare. I dare.

11:30.706 --> 11:31.608
You know what?
Actually, I dare you.

11:31.641 --> 11:33.545
-I dare right now.
-I dare you. Call Mom.

11:33.578 --> 11:34.948
-Uh-huh.
-I dare you. Call Mom.

11:34.981 --> 11:36.017
-Mom.
-I'm gonna call--

11:36.050 --> 11:37.052
-Call Mom. Call Mom.
-Mom. Mom.

11:37.085 --> 11:37.987
-See what happens.
